# Experiment output. See CLAUDE.md section 7 for the storage policy.
#   results/raw/       large per-run rows, regenerable from script + seed -> ignored
#   results/summaries/ compact aggregates consumed by the report + figures -> committed
results/raw/
!results/summaries/
!results/summaries/*.csv
!results/summaries/*.parquet

